and we get a three minute
increment for each move.

7
00:00:25,680 --> 00:00:29,503
[We] play this very natural opening
he plays the Albin Counter Gambit,

8
00:00:30,210 --> 00:00:35,285
which is technically a bit
dubious, but very very playable

9
