69
00:04:25,232 --> 00:04:27,252
I going to bring out the Rooks;

70
00:04:27,277 --> 00:04:31,282
I'm going to firebomb his
pawns; they're all going to blow up;

71
00:04:31,307 --> 00:04:35,675
he's going to have an open
King; his Rook is nowhere;

72
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:40,480
his Queen is almost nowhere.
It's just really looking bad for him.

73
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:44,645
So I went to make this move,

74
00:04:44,670 --> 00:04:49,055
