miscalibrated; maybe I was so excited;

75
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:54,725
whatever reason; instead of making
this move I ended up accidentally making...

76
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,255
THIS move;

77
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:59,356
