81
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:18,245
Takebacks are
not well thought of.

82
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:21,450
It can be abused: you make a move; you look
at the position; you don't like it; you say

83
00:05:21,450 --> 00:05:24,126
<i>No, no, no, I'm going to do this other
