a game that never ends.

85
00:05:29,370 --> 00:05:33,169
But this case it was obvious
that I meant to do Qb7.

86
00:05:33,194 --> 00:05:34,953
It's the only move
that makes any sense

87
00:05:34,977 --> 00:05:37,642
that could possibly have
mouse-slipped to this,

88
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:42,425
and my opponent said <i>No</i>.

89
00:05:42,450 --> 00:05:45,903
I don't fault my opponent for this. I would
have done the same thing in his situation.

90
00:05:45,928 --> 00:05:47,975
We're playing a blitz game.

91
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,582
This is a rated
game, and in blitz,

92
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:54,037
