the takeback) he has to move.

95
00:06:00,544 --> 00:06:03,185
There's only one
move he legally has.

96
00:06:03,210 --> 00:06:04,465
He has to deal with this check.

97
00:06:04,489 --> 00:06:06,956
The only way to deal with
the check is to take the Queen.

98
00:06:06,981 --> 00:06:09,815
Now he's up a Queen.

99
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:17,037
So I've gone from the
computer saying <i>+11.3</i>,

100
00:06:18,847 --> 00:06:20,435
because of Qb7+,

101
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:25,304
to <i>-9.4</i>. I've lost twenty
points of material.

102
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,211
Two Queens.

103
00:06:29,235 --> 00:06:32,178
I've gone from being effectively a
Queen up, to being a Queen down.

104
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:40,955
