to have to develop his Queen somehow.

109
00:06:56,222 --> 00:07:01,475
Uh, there's no prayer of a draw.

110
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:04,025
Certainly no way to win.

111
00:07:04,050 --> 00:07:07,574
But I'm not thinking rationally.
I've just blundered my queen,

112
00:07:07,599 --> 00:07:09,759
due to a mouseslip;

113
00:07:09,784 --> 00:07:12,892
I've asked for takeback;
